6張 <br />\n但係入落機到少咗幾張 正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82031b39ada8eb7cd9f5dd8bc9e14f8162845f60","tid":1890262,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff3cd257dc2bcee38c70cb70904688060c5483f9","tid":1890262,"uid":214238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"我新手都想問下 <br />\n部機係自動上片 買菲林有36張 <br />\n但係入落機到少咗幾張 正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T17:48:58.000Z","msg":"一筒36張基本上手動過片機影到38.5張，有時39<br />\n自動過片嘅gr1v都有37<br />\n你部機連36都無，壞撚咗"},{"pid":"5dcd4c78e685fb5ba5709b3f2af5c134b97bcb24","tid":1890262,"uid":8684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"攞張底片睇下咪知咩事<br />\n如果成條冇左-&gt;間鋪整唔見（好少可）<br />\n如果有幾格係白片-&gt;快門冇開 / 冇開鏡頭蓋 / 太暗冇開閃光燈等等都有可能"}]}